<title>ạlqlb kfạyth wạḥd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạlqlb kfạyth wạḥd yạ nfsy ạ̉ʿqly
 ạ̉syạdk lyh ktyr ʿly̱ myn btdwry?)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạlḥạjh ạ̹ly̱ wạḥd wnrwḥ lgẖyrh lyh?
 ạlḥạjh ạ̹ly̱ wạḥd mn gẖyrh nʿml ạ̉yh?)2
 2- (sạmḥny wqwl lnfsy mgẖfwrh lk kẖṭạyạk
 ṣwtk byfk ḥbsy lmsạtk fwq ạ̹drạky)2
 3- (ạ̹nt ạlnṣyb ạlṣạlḥ lyk ạ̉ksr ạlqạrwrh
 ạ̹ydyk tʿwd tṣlḥ dẖạty ạlʿạṣyh ạlmgẖrwrh)2</lyrics>
</song>